title: There is No Other Option
itunes:title: There is No Other Option
description:
Episode 547 -  How committed are you to your goals? Are you pretty committed? Are you kinda committed? Or are you either going to hit your goals or die? These are a very important questions because most people don't realize that success takes a certain level of dedication that most people are not willing to give. Check out this episode to learn more!
